  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SWORN is a 1-4 player co-op action rogue-like. Explore and reclaim a fallen Camelot from the reign of a corrupted Arthur and his Knights of the Round Table.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763250/extras/b5acb1bd2bc0361fe03601a90bc84040.avif?t=1774363714\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763250/extras_big/b5acb1bd2bc0361fe03601a90bc84040.avif?t=1774363714 width=800 height=414 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763250/extras/ed9450099398c8c7ec4418aaf91ece0d.avif?t=1774363714\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Play solo or unite with friends to stand off against the Knights of the Round Table. Combine the strengths of your characters in surprising ways and master abilities to become knights worthy of standing off against Arthur himself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763250/extras/d39f0b2a34f52cbcefcdbcf67a0dded2.poster.avif?t=1774363714\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763250/extras/d39f0b2a34f52cbcefcdbcf67a0dded2.webm?t=1774363714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763250/extras/85c30b28b2c00dc02e430e79c3a2a654.avif?t=1774363714\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet familiar friends and foes from Arthurian legend.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the source of spreading darkness over Avalon.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Befriend and learn from powerful figures such as Merlin and Nimue. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take up your sword as a Soulforged knight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763250/extras/62e4a3db87b497d2c54771db7b315ca9.avif?t=1774363714\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763250/extras_big/62e4a3db87b497d2c54771db7b315ca9.avif?t=1774363714 width=800 height=414 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763250/extras/ca9456b7d309183b79748074b6546813.avif?t=1774363714\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763250/extras/ea5826acb290afe739e0b26756d93f33.poster.avif?t=1774363714\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763250/extras/ea5826acb290afe739e0b26756d93f33.webm?t=1774363714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Swear fealty to the Fae Lords, and choose from over 200 unique blessings to unleash your full potential. Will you wield the cleansing fires of Titania or take the blessings of Oberon to strike with the fury of the wind?  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                               </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763250/extras/9642bda11bd9b382b8ba27c09c2deabc.avif?t=1774363714\" width=600 height=210 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763250/extras/fb47e4fd36cf9d90eb54fc7c230a2de4.avif?t=1774363714\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763250/extras/0fdf36389eab493698e4d30f231a6ae1.poster.avif?t=1774363714\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763250/extras/0fdf36389eab493698e4d30f231a6ae1.webm?t=1774363714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Versatility thrives in the ever-changing battlegrounds of Camelot. Combine your blessings with unique character, weapon, and ability selections. Test thousands of unique builds as you become a seasoned knight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763250/extras/b999954e3f61c8e072249b7681b9f22f.avif?t=1774363714\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763250/extras_big/b999954e3f61c8e072249b7681b9f22f.avif?t=1774363714 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763250/extras/3b0f529cf7201f241589ca35db2a5b84.avif?t=1774363714\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Upgrades from the Beacon of Avalore will forge your squire into a worthy champion over time. However, if you believe you are already worthy of facing Arthur, get ready for a challenge that will put your skills to the test.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763250/extras/0019a5c49b2aa300bf2e47c76b9f5909.poster.avif?t=1774363714\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763250/extras/0019a5c49b2aa300bf2e47c76b9f5909.webm?t=1774363714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763250/extras/a55ed015487b2968c0cbf80947e71afb.avif?t=1774363714\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Delve into a beautifully crafted comic world, inspired by the work of American artist Mike Mignola. Fully experience the awesome art and original sound that brings the world of SWORN to life.</p>",
